    Class Description
    Battleship
    Loads and launches the Battleship game
    BattleshipController
    Main class for the game Battleship
    BoardState
    This class tracks the state of a grid for a Battleship player, validates guesses, and also tracks what boats have or can be placed on the board.
    BoatOrientations
    Contains possible boat orientations when designing
    Client
    This class initializes the UI for the cli
    ClientHandler
    Handler which runs on its own thread in order to handle server requests from the client it is currently connected to
    ClientPanel
    This class initializes the UI for the Battleship client
    Config
    This class defines various constants that is to be used by the Server and Client to standardize communication
    Constants
    This class constants shared Constants that are used in multiple classes or packages
    DesignState  
    EventPanel
    This class is displays the history log for guesses, option selections, and general info to the user
    GameState
    This class represents the current state of the game and tracks turns, score, and current status/phase of the game
    GameStatus
    Contains various statuses representing what stage the game is in
    GridBoat
    Represents a boat of a given size during the design phase
    GridPanel
    This class creates and initializes a grid of buttons used for a player's Battleship game board
    GridSquare
    Represents a square on the battleship grid
    GridSquareStatus
    Contains statuses that a grid square may have
    HealthBarsPanel  
    MainPanel
    This class creates and initializes the main panel which includes the game boards, event log, and options menu
    MenuBar
    This class creates the primary menu bar for the game which contains extra options not displayed in the main window
    OptionsPanel
    Creates the options panel for the Battleship game
    Server
    This class contains the backend logic for the Battleship server
    ServerPanel  
    SplashScreens
    This class displays various splashscreens for different parts of the game
    Utils
    This class contains methods to perform useful operations or actions used by multiple classes in the project
